---
title: Indian Chicken & Creamy Red Lentil Curry with Crispy Flatbreads
description: This creamy chicken curry gets a wholesome boost from lentils, which are a great source of protein and fibre. But best of all, they give extra texture and make it not just delicious, but totally and utterly satisfying.

*Unfortunately, this week's courgette was in short supply, so we've replaced it with baby spinach leaves. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
